## How to Contribute

We welcome contributions from the community! If you'd like to get involved:

- Refer to [CONTRIBUTING.md](https://github.com/naval-group/LOTUSim/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md) for more info
- Report bugs or request features via [Issues](../../issues)
- Submit improvements via pull request
- For partnership inquiries, contact [lotusim_support@naval-group.com](mailto:lotusim_support@naval-group.com)

Thank you to everyone who has contributed to LOTUSim! :)
